{"tid":1538701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要］依家先嚟講撒回？","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:28:39.000Z","uid":27719,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee14474bd88dfbec069477d7b54e096d684c188","tid":1538701,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"眾所周知<br />\n<br />\n9月9日報美國國會復會，基本上 Hong Kong and demoracty act 就一定會通過<br />\n<br />\n依個時候講撒回， 若果香港人接受，打哂飛機講咩「階段性勝利」，可能會導致兩黨分裂，會令保守黨嘅人（指偏向同中國合作, instead of對立）覺得「香港人都接受咗，咁唔洗再搞啦」<br />\n<br />\n另外 之前Trump trump 提供一枚有關 「清朝十萬億債券」嘅核彈，暫時嚟連登文宣係「好撚少」 <br />\n<br />\n依個關主權係屬於「中華民國」 定「中國共產黨」 係好大分別，中國唔肯還即係話香港仲係屬於大清，而繼承大清正統，袁世凱去咗台灣，所以不論法律上，歷史上，中華民國先係英國還地嘅對象並唔係中共<br />\n<br />\n中共所講《中英聯合聲明》 係歷史文件係無錯<br />\n因為真「唔關」佢地事，但對「中華民國」嚟講就關佢事兼具法律約束力<br />\n<br />\n中共係「非法」霸佔香港<br />\n<br />\nTrump Trump係啲仆街商人講嘅，一定會 benefit自己，我地可不順水推舟，助佢一臂之力達成自己目標<br />\n<br />\n再者，大家如果「袋住先」，其實訴求一定，係一定唔會再爭取到<br />\n<br />\n林奠係幾咁奸狡，大家有目共睹，唔講五年前雨革<br />\n皇后碼頭，囍帖街 都係大家引以為鑑，活生生嘅好例子<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪想再等多五年？香港人仲有幾多個五年？<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得 GanstapoHK 係點對我地， 831 前幾日咋，屌哂你地老母， 無差別毆打市民呀， 係咪死撚咗人都未知呀！<br />\n<br />\n仲有811，721，612 呢，吓，洗唔洗睇返巴絲整理嘅事件薄温返下書呀<br />\n<br />\n幾個手足無咗隻眼呀，酷刑，性侵/非禮手足呀，屌哂你地老母<br />\n<br />\n比階段性勝利沖昏哂頭腦呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結： <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">差一個我都唔撚要呀， Package嚟㗎</span></span><br />\n知唔知咩叫Package 呀， 叉燒飯剩係比飯你唔比叉燒你，叫唔叫叉燒飯呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkNVOmR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkNVOmR.png&h=81687250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好對唔住手足呀</span></span><br />\n唔好原諒啲狗 ！We never forgive we never forget j"},{"pid":"3bbe6474f239d724c755ed3117131754aec857b2","tid":1538701,"uid":147345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"bdfcde99356ebb6bdef1afa220339917d5ccefc3","tid":1538701,"uid":314195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"無錯啊<br />\n仲有幾多個五年！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林奠真係好奸</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好軟化啊 香港人！</span><br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831"},{"pid":"1a00216760fec9273e46f4a9146bcdcea0cf412c","tid":1538701,"uid":314195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">907機場交通壓力測試</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnHKGKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnHKGKx.jpg&h=cd059c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">908美國駐港總領事館</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkXuSQW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkXuSQW.jpg&h=eecd8842&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOgocQW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOgocQW.jpg&h=b9af224f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGXFZwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGXFZwh.jpg&h=9068b638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a191bfe6d195e2cd9ab51b0a7d9519782c0e670","tid":1538701,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n612、721、811、831 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6254119da705d44d6d29706706374