ec633877b871bc0cc5866310ca8d9b84dfddc1","tid":1538701,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n但我唔想每一次都要抗爭政府先會聽我講野<br />\n所以寫左係基本法既雙普選係一定要有！<br />\n若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變到做到喇<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"7d0aaba1e91d1de746019d6bfc7eb8da403ef35c","tid":1538701,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nbin個袋住先我就同bin個割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df0d34371a844a83cb405b40224d57a96a8595e","tid":1538701,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"A fucking package <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c385b520087d9fc084bd29659437650c23285692","tid":1538701,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n答呀"}]}